        "code": "```yaml\nframework:\n    messenger:\n        failure_transport: failed\n        transports:\n            async:\n                dsn: '%env(MESSENGER_TRANSPORT_DSN)%'\n                failure_transport: failed\n            failed:\n                dsn: '%env(MESSENGER_TRANSPORT_DSN)%'\n                options: { queue_name: failed }"
